data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Holland! This beautifully renovated 3-bedroom, 1-bath residence offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm. Located just a short stroll from downtown Holland, this gem is within walking distance to Kollen Park and close to downtown Holland making it an ideal place for those who appreciate convenience with easy access to shops, restaurants, and entertainment! Don't miss the opportunity to make this renovated beauty your new home! Schedule a viewing today and envision the lifestyle that awaits you in this delightful home!
